{"word":"G170 - ἀκαιρέομαι - akairéomai - ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee - Lack opportunity","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκαιρέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">akairéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lack opportunity</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சமயம்"},{"paragraph":"to lack opportunity"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2540 - καιρός - kairós - kahee-ros'/2540\">G2540</a> (meaning <i>unseasonable</i>); to <i>be inopportune</i> (for oneself), that is, to <i>fail of a proper occasion:</i> - lack opportunity.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G170/170\">G170</a>, <a href=\"#/G171/171\">G171</a>, <a href=\"#/G2120/2120\">G2120</a>, <a href=\"#/G2121/2121\">G2121</a>, <a href=\"#/G2122/2122\">G2122</a>, <a href=\"#/G2540/2540\">G2540</a>, <a href=\"#/G4340/4340\">G4340</a>"}]}